Resource Profile: PPL Ingredient profile

Official URL: http://unicom-project.eu/fhir/StructureDefinition/PPLIngredient Version: 0.1.0
Active as of 2022-11-18 Computable Name: PPLIngredient

Ingredient for the medicinal product, pharmaceutical product and/or manufactured item

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Ingredient/Agen-5mg-Tablet-EE-I, Ingredient/CanifugCremolum-100mg-Pessary-EE-I, Ingredient/CanifugCremolum-10mg1g-Cream-EE-I

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.
